Simplest solution would be to include a `should` clause along with the `must` clause and in the `should` clause you only mention the logic of having students **`with BE but without MS or PhD`**. 

All this in your [Boolean Query][1]

Note that `must` is metaphorically similar to `AND` logic while `should` would be an `OR`.

Once that is done, you can simply add the logic in [`Sort`][2] (as mentioned in the link) to *first* sort using `_score` then to sort based on *`Education.endDate`* field.

Below is how the solution would be:

    POST students/_search
    {
      &quot;query&quot;: {
        &quot;bool&quot;: {
          &quot;must&quot;: [
            {
              &quot;match&quot; :{
                &quot;StudentName&quot;: &quot;student&quot;
              }
            }
          ], 
          &quot;should&quot;: [
            {
              &quot;bool&quot;: {
                &quot;must&quot;: [
                  {
                    &quot;nested&quot;: {
                      &quot;path&quot;: &quot;Education&quot;,
                      &quot;query&quot;: {
                        &quot;terms&quot;: {
                          &quot;Education.degreeName.keyword&quot;: [
                            &quot;BE&quot;
                          ]
                        }
                      }
                    }
                  }
                ],
                &quot;must_not&quot;: [
                  {
                    &quot;nested&quot;: {
                      &quot;path&quot;: &quot;Education&quot;,
                      &quot;query&quot;: {
                        &quot;terms&quot;: {
                          &quot;Education.degreeName.keyword&quot;: [
                            &quot;MS&quot;,
                            &quot;PhD&quot;
                          ]
                        }
                      }
                    }
                  }
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      &quot;sort&quot;: [
        { &quot;_score&quot; : { &quot;order&quot;: &quot;desc&quot;}},
        {
          &quot;Education.endDate&quot;: {
            &quot;order&quot;: &quot;desc&quot;
          }
        }
      ]
    }

Let me know if this helps!

  [1]: https://www.elastic.co/guide/en/elasticsearch/reference/current/query-dsl-bool-query.html
  [2]: https://www.elastic.co/guide/en/elasticsearch/reference/6.2/search-request-sort.html

